to celebrate would be to...

1502
02:07:25,221 --> 02:07:27,973
...make a donation to help a healer
named Wayan Nuriyasih...

1503
02:07:28,141 --> 02:07:30,267
...buy a house in Indonesia.

1504
02:07:30,435 --> 02:07:33,603
She's a single mother.
ln Bali, after a divorce...

1505
02:07:33,771 --> 02:07:36,523
