not even her children.

1506
02:07:36,691 --> 02:07:40,735
To gain custody of her daughter, Tutti,
Wayan had to sell everything...

1507
02:07:40,903 --> 02:07:43,447
...even her bath mat,
to pay for a lawyer.

1508
02:07:44,449 --> 02:07:46,450
For years,
they've moved from place to place.

1509
02:07:46,659 --> 02:07:50,287
Each time, Wayan loses clientele
and Tutti has to change schools.

1510
02:07:51,205 --> 02:07:55,125
This little group of people in Bali
have become my family.

1511
02:07:55,293 --> 02:07:58,795
And we must take care of our
families, wherever we find them.

1512
02:07:58,963 --> 02:08:02,299
Today l saw Tutti playing with
a blue tile she'd found in the road...

1513
02:08:02,467 --> 02:08:05,135
...near a hotel construction site.
She told me:

1514
02:08:05,303 --> 02:08:07,971
Maybe if we have
a house someday...

1515
02:08:08,181 --> 02:08:10,974
...it can have a pretty blue floor
like this.

1516
02:08:11,809 --> 02:08:13,602
When I was in Italy,
I learned a word--

1517
02:08:13,769 --> 02:08:15,020
It's "tutti" with double T.

1518
02:08:15,980 --> 02:08:20,442
--which in ltalian means "everybody."
So that's the lesson, isn't it?

1519
02:08:20,610 --> 02:08:23,153
When you set out in the world
to help yourself...

1520
02:08:23,321 --> 02:08:25,614
...sometimes you end up
helping Tutti.

1521
02:08:28,951 --> 02:08:32,162
-Tell me again.
-Eighteen thousand American dollars.

1522
02:08:32,330 --> 02:08:34,998
I brought you the e-mails to look at.

1523
02:08:37,460 --> 02:08:38,668
Oh, my God.

1524
02:08:38,836 --> 02:08:40,128
We get a house.

1525
02:08:40,296 --> 02:08:43,507
It can be the house for everybody!

1526
02:08:45,510 --> 02:08:48,845
I can have a pharmacy!
I can have a library!

1527
02:08:50,014 --> 02:08:52,682
-All right. Oh, God.
-Close them again. Close your eyes.

1528
02:08:52,850 --> 02:08:55,185
