1558
02:10:35,620 --> 02:10:37,120
...by ourselves...

1559
02:10:37,288 --> 02:10:41,625
...apart from everything else for
a couple of days, is that much for you?

1560
02:10:41,834 --> 02:10:44,878
Liz, não entendo.
What's the problem, Liz?

1561
02:10:45,046 --> 02:10:48,715
I mean, l have the same fears,
I have the same scars that you have...

1562
02:10:48,883 --> 02:10:50,925
...and l show them to you.

1563
02:10:51,093 --> 02:10:54,721
But l guess the only difference
between you and l is that...

1564
02:10:55,097 --> 02:10:56,806
...you are afraid to love again.

1565
02:10:56,974 --> 02:10:58,350
My darling, this is it.

1566
02:10:58,726 --> 02:11:01,645
You have to look me in the eye
and let me know the truth.

1567
02:11:02,271 --> 02:11:06,107
Please. Do you love me
or do you love me not?

1568
02:11:10,154 --> 02:11:11,738
Look me in the eyes and tell me...

1569
02:11:11,906 --> 02:11:15,367
...do you love me or don't
you love me not? lt's very easy.

1570
02:11:15,951 --> 02:11:18,495
I know you feel the same way.
