1571
02:11:18,663 --> 02:11:20,747
I don't know why.

1572
02:11:22,792 --> 02:11:24,000
Why can't l?

1573
02:11:24,168 --> 02:11:27,504
Because you're terrified, my love.
But listen, it's fine. Me too.

1574
02:11:27,880 --> 02:11:30,840
But l still want to get
into that boat with you.

1575
02:11:31,008 --> 02:11:33,510
-No. Okay, look. Look.
-What?

1576
02:11:33,678 --> 02:11:36,680
I don't know why
you can't understand this.

1577
02:11:36,889 --> 02:11:40,433
I found something
and l can't give it up.

1578
02:11:40,601 --> 02:11:44,854
