going to see an old medicine man?

1582
02:11:55,491 --> 02:11:59,202
Listen, balance, my darling, balance
is not letting anybody love you...

1583
02:11:59,412 --> 02:12:02,372
-...less than you love yourself.
-You know what? You know what?

1584
02:12:02,540 --> 02:12:06,459
Do not tell me what lessons l have
and haven't learned in the last year...

1585
02:12:06,627 --> 02:12:09,045
...and don't tell me how balanced
and wise you are...

1586
02:12:09,213 --> 02:12:11,548
...and how I can't express myself.

1587
02:12:11,716 --> 02:12:15,385
And do not say "darling" to me again
because l am just gonna lose it.

1588
02:12:15,553 --> 02:12:19,848
Listen to me! l do not need to love you
to prove that l love myself.

1589
02:12:26,814 --> 02:12:28,732
